  "title": "QA Assistant | Lab Inspector | Chemical Manufacturing (MNC) | West",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is a Manufacturing MNC for Chemical Materials. Due to business needs, they are now recruiting a Lab Technologist to be part of their Lab Team for ongoing transformation projects. They are located in the West - easily accessible.</strong></p><p><strong>Duties of Lab Technologist:</strong></p><ul><li>Conduct sampling, inspection, testing, and release of raw materials, in-process, and finished goods to ensure compliance with specifications.</li><li>Handle sample receipt, labeling, storage, and review of Certificates of Analysis.</li><li>Maintain and calibrate laboratory equipment, ensuring accuracy and reliability of test results.</li><li>Monitor lab inventory and support smooth daily operations.</li><li>Report and manage quality or safety non-conformances, including issuing NC forms to suppliers.</li><li>Support internal/external audits and ensure compliance with QEHSMS, safety, and 5S standards.</li><li>Perform additional tasks as assigned by the QA Manager.</li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements:</strong></h3><ul><li>Diploma or Degree in Chemical related field</li><li>1-2 years of lab/QA experience in chemical or relevant industry</li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click <strong>APPLY NOW</strong> or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><ul><li><strong>Email Address: jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></li><li>EA License No: 19C9682</li><li>EA Personnel No: R2198636 (Oh Puey Xin)</li></ul>",
